    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Yup, this is exactly why we recommend against using `--pylab` as of IPython 1.0, and will disable `--pylab` (in the notebook) in 3.0.\n\nFor historical reasons, `--pylab` and `%pylab` will probably not go away, but they should be absent from IPython's docs, so they may die a slow, quiet death.\n"
